      <h2 class="post"><a href="/2013/03/08/validatr-pointeraccuracy-testacular">Validatr, pointeraccuracy.js, Testacular Updates</a></h2>

<div class="meta">
  08 Mar 2013 |
  <span class="author">By Alex Young</span> |
  <span class="tags">
